Ok, I think I got it working but by no means am I an expert at this stuff... Got the idea from another driver genius torrent:

1) Install as CC's info says
2) Update so you get the latest files
3) After that update, you have to reinstall the crack as the update changes that back to the program's original
4) Run program, should hopefully be cracked and updated now

Those steps may not be exactly the 'best' way to do it, but it worked for me - just updated 19 drivers. 

So it looks like you can update, just remember to replace the crack each time. Not a big deal since you probably don't need to be running driver updates often.
